## Problem 1
```{r}
nrow(count(instacart,aisle))
instacart %>%
  group_by(aisle) %>%
  count()%>%
  arrange(desc(n)) 
```

There are 134 aisles in this dataset and the aisle that most order from is fresh vegetables

```{r}
instacart %>% 
  count(aisle)%>%
  filter(n>10000) %>%
  arrange(desc(n))%>%
  ggplot(aes(y=n, color=aisle))+geom_boxplot()
```
